version_description: I'm playing a little intro right before the first verse. In the original Milow is strumming the bridge. But I think with a little pause between the chorus and bridge, it sounds awesome to continue with some fingerpicking. The strumming pattern is suitable for the verse, just listen and get the groove. In the chorus my strumming pattern is mainly improvised.
